pageTitle: High School Sports | Aug. 19 2011 football Mountain Crest-Provo | Deseret News
textBeforeTable: Rushing Individual stats Mountain Crest quarterback Eddy Hall rushed for a touchdown and passed for another to lead the Mustangs to an easy victory over the Bulldogs. Provo went out with a bang as KC Henson hauled in an 84-yard bomb from Christian Brown for the final score of the game.
